extensionName.message: Extensión de navegador de Contrasinais para Nextcloud

SettingsAutofillIgnoredDomains.message: Ignorar estes dominios (un por liña, tamén se ignoran os subdominios)
SettingsAutofillIgnoredDomains.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to maintain a list of domains where the extension should not autofill passwords. The textarea should be filled with one domain per line, no spaces. Subdomains of the listed domains will also be ignored automatically.

extensionDescription.message: A extensión de navegador oficial de Contrasinais para Nextcloud

locale.description: The language tag of this translation. Same as the folder name

browserActionTitle.description: Title of the button in the browser bar

contextMenuTitle.description: Title of the context menu item

BrowserActionTitleCounter.description: Title of the button in the browser bar with suggestion counter

MigrationAccountName.description: Label assigned to the account used by the v1.x migration

PrivatePasswordsFolderLabel.description: Label assigned to the hidden folder for private passwords. (folder is only visible when browsing in private mode)

SettingsTabAccounts.description: Label of the user accounts tab in the extension settings

SettingsTabTheming.description: Label of the themes tab in the extension settings

SettingsTabOther.description: Label of the general settings tab in the extension settings

SettingsTabDebug.description: Label of the extension debugging tab in the extension settings

SettingsAccountsMain.description: Label of the option to choose the main account in the extension settings. This account will be used to synchronize settings accross apps, store new passwords and so on

AutofillSettings.description: Headline above the password autofill section in the other settings tab in the extension settings

SettingsPastePopupClose.message: Pechar a xanela emerxente após pegar as credenciais
SettingsPastePopupClose.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to automatically close the extension popup after successful pasting

SettingsPasteWarnCompromised.message: Advertir cando se empreguen credenciais comprometidas
SettingsPasteWarnCompromised.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to show a warning after pasting a compromised password

SettingsPasteAutofillEnabled.message: Encher automaticamente os datos de acceso que correspondan
SettingsPasteAutofillEnabled.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to automatically paste the first recommended credential into login forms

SettingsPasteBasicAuth.message: Responder automaticamente ás solicitudes de autenticación básica HTTP
SettingsPasteBasicAuth.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to automatically respond with the first recommended credential to any http basic authentication request

HelpPasteBasicAuth.message: Responde automaticamente ás solicitudes de autenticación básica http coa primeira credencial suxerida. Teña en conta que isto pode expoñer as credenciais a servidores pouco fiábeis.
HelpPasteBasicAuth.description: Help text in the extension settings for the setting to automatically respond with the first recommended credential to any http basic authentication request

SettingsClearClipboardPasswords.message: Eliminar automaticamente os contrasinais do portapapeis
SettingsClearClipboardPasswords.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to automatically clear passwords from clipboard after a certain time.

SettingsClearClipboardDelay.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to define the time when the clipboard content will be removed.

SettingsClipboardClearDelayOptions.description: Time in seconds until clipboard will get empty.

SettingsNotifyPasswordNew.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to enable or disable the notification for new detected passwords

SettingsNotifyPasswordQuicksave.message: Gardar ou actualizar os contrasinais directamente cando se preme na notificación
SettingsNotifyPasswordQuicksave.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to save or update a password directly when the related notification is clicked

SearchSettings.description: Headline above the search section in the other settings tab in the extension settings

PasswordMiningSettings.description: Headline above the password mining section in the other settings tab in the extension settings

SettingsMiningIgnoredDomains.message: Ignorar estes dominios (un por liña, tamén se ignoran os subdominios)
SettingsMiningIgnoredDomains.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to maintain a list of domains where the extension should not detect new or changed passwords. The textarea should be filled with one domain per line, no spaces. Subdomains of the listed domains will also be ignored automatically.

TabRelated.description: Label of the related passwords tab in the extension popup

SettingsMiningIncognitoHide.message: Almacenar os contrasinais recompilados en Incógnito como contrasinais privados
SettingsMiningIncognitoHide.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to enable or disable switching to the search tab in the popup if the user types in the related passwords tab

AccountList.description: Headline above the user accounts section in the accounts tab in the extension settings

NoAccounts.message: Aínda non hai contas. Prema aquí para crear unha.
NoAccounts.description: Message in place of the user accounts list in the extension settings if there are no user accounts yet. The user can click the message to create an account

FirstRunServerCheckTitle.description: Title of the first run wizard settings page while data is loaded from the server

FirstRunSettingsTitle.description: Title of the first run wizard page that allows the user to change some common settings

LabelGeneratorStrengthUltra.description: Label of the very high (4) strength option for the password generator in the tools tab

LabelGeneratorStrengthLow.description: Label of the low (0) strength option for the password generator in the tools tab

LabelGeneratorStrengthStandard.description: Label of the default (1) strength option for the password generator in the tools tab

LabelGeneratorStrengthMedium.description: Label of the medium (2) strength option for the password generator in the tools tab

LabelGeneratorStrengthHigh.description: Label of the high (3) strength option for the password generator in the tools tab

LabelGenerateAddSpecial.description: Label of the option to include special characters in the password generator in the tools tab

LabelGenerateStrength.description: Label of the option to set the strength in the password generator in the tools tab

LabelGenerateAddNumbers.description: Label of the option to include numbers in the password generator in the tools tab

GeneratedPasswordPlaceholder.description: Placeholder of the field for the generated password in the tools tab of the popup

ToolsTabGeneratePassword.description: Label of the generate password section in the tools tab of the popup

ToolsTabDebugTools.description: Label of the debugging tools section in the tools tab of the popup

FirstRunSettingsSave.description: Text of the button in the first run wizard to save the settings and close the wizard

SettingsPasteFormSubmit.message: Enviar formularios de acceso cando se peguen as credenciais dende a xanela emerxente
SettingsPasteFormSubmit.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to automatically submit login forms after pasting

NotificationSettings.description: Headline above the notification section in the other settings tab in the extension settings (!Currently Unused)

DebugResetStatisticsTitle.message: Restabelece as estatísticas de uso recompiladas utilizadas para recomendar credenciais na lapela relacionada
DebugResetStatisticsTitle.description: Help title text of the button to reset the usage statistics for the password recommendations in the debug tab in the extension settings

UserAgent.message: Cliente oficial de Contrasinais para $BROWSER$ en $OS$
UserAgent.description: The user agent used for api requests. Only ASCII characters allowed: 0-9, A-Z, a-z. No special characters or non latin characters like ä,á,ã or ß

SettingsNotifyPasswordUpdate.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to enable or disable the notification for detected password updates

SettingsPopupRelatedSearch.message: Comezar a busca cando escriba en «Relacionado»
SettingsPopupRelatedSearch.description: Label of the setting in the extension settings to enable or disable switching to the search tab in the popup if the user types in the related passwords tab

ServerTimeoutOptionMinutes.description: Label of the option for the server timeout to expire after a given amount of minutes

HelpPasteAutofill.message: Pega automaticamente a primeira credencial suxerida en calquera formulario de acceso da lapela. Teña en conta que isto fai que sexa accesíbel calquera script da lapela.
HelpPasteAutofill.description: Help text in the extension settings for the setting to automatically paste credentials into login forms

HelpClearClipboardPasswords.message: O portapapeis só se limpará se o navegador aínda está aberto. Se se concede o permiso opcional para ler o portapapeis, só se limpará se o contrasinal aínda está alí.
HelpClearClipboardPasswords.description: Help text in the extension settings for the setting to automatically clean passwords from clipboard after a certain time.

NoRelatedPasswords.description: Used in the related tab when no entries match the current website

FirstRunSetupManually.description: Text of the button or link in the first run wizard to open the settings and add an account manually

NewAccountFormLabel.description: Label of the new account form in the extension settings

ServerSaveTitle.description: Title of the toast notification in the extension settings after an account was created or updated successfully

ServerSaveMessage.description: Message of the toast notification in the extension settings after an account was created successfully

ServerCreatedMessage.message: Foi creada a conta e está lista para ser usada
ServerCreatedMessage.description: Message of the toast notification in the extension settings after an account was updated successfully

ServerSaveErrorTitle.description: Title of the toast notification in the extension settings after an account could not be updated or saved. The message will be the specific error message

ServerDisabledWarning.message: Esta conta está desactivada. Activarase após que se garde correctamente.
ServerDisabledWarning.description: Warning message which appears above the account details if the server was disabled. Usual reasons are invalid login data, unsupported extension version or permanent connection issues.

ServerLabel.description: Label of the account name field in account details in the extension settings

ServerBaseUrl.description: Label of the server url field in account details in the extension settings

ServerUser.description: Label of the account login user field in account details in the extension settings

ServerToken.description: Label of the account login token field in account details in the extension settings

ServerTokenChange.description: Label of the button to change the login token of an existing account in the account details in the extension settings

ServerTimeout.description: Label of the option to change the automatic logout time of an existing account in the account details in the extension settings

ServerTimeoutOptionNever.description: Label of the option for the server timeout to never expire

TabSearch.description: Label of the search tab in the extension popup

TabBrowse.description: Label of the browse servers tab in the extension popup

TabCollected.description: Label of the new collected passwords tab in the extension popup

TabTools.description: Label of the tools tab in the extension popup

PasswordItemTitle.description: The tooltip of any password entry in the popup

PasswordItemOpenUrl.description: Title of the menu option to open the password url in a new tab

PasswordItemToTrash.description: Title of the menu option to move a password to the trash

PasswordItemDetails.description: Title of the menu option to view and edit a password

ValidationLabel.description: Name of the account label field in account validation message. This value is used when the user attempts to save an account with an invalid label

ValidationUser.description: Name of the account username field in account validation message. This value is used when the user attempts to save an account with an invalid username

ValidationBaseUrl.description: Name of the account base url field in account validation message. This value is used when the user attempts to save an account with an invalid base url

ValidationNotEmpty.message: O campo $FIELD$ non pode estar baleiro.
ValidationNotEmpty.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save something (like an account) but a required field is empty.

ValidationMinLength.message: O campo $FIELD$ debe ter polo menos $MIN$ caracteres.
ValidationMinLength.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save something (like an account) but a field is shorter than required

ValidationMaxLength.message: O campo $FIELD$ debe ter menos de $MAX$ caracteres.
ValidationMaxLength.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save something (like an account) but a field is longer than allowed

ValidationFailed.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save something (like an account) but there were validation errors

ValidationNotAnUrl.message: O URL base debe ser un URL válido.
ValidationNotAnUrl.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save an account but the server url is not a valid url

ValidationNotAToken.message: O contrasinal da aplicación debe ser un contrasinal de aplicación Nextcloud válido.
ValidationNotAToken.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save an account but the token does not match the Nextcloud token schema

ValidationDuplicate.message: Xa hai unha conta para este usuario neste Nextcloud.
ValidationDuplicate.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save a new account, but a similar account with the same server and same user name already exists

ValidationUnauthorizedError.message: O servidor en $URL$ non aceptou os datos de acceso.
ValidationUnauthorizedError.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save an account but the server did not accept the user name and token

ValidationHttpError.message: Ao tentar conectarse a $URL$ produciuse o erro $ERROR$.
ValidationHttpError.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save an account but the server responded with an unexpected HTTP status code

ValidationNoConnection.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save an account but it is not possible to connect to this server with the given url

ValidationServerVersion.message: A versión da aplicación instalada no servidor está desactualizada.
ValidationServerVersion.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save an account but the version of the passwords app installed on the server is outdated

TitleClickToEdit.description: Tooltip used in the collected password form for any property of the password to inform the user that double clicking makes the text field editable

TitleEnterToExit.description: Tooltip used in the collected password form to tell the user that the property can be saved by clicking enter

NoSearchResults.message: Non foi atopado ningún contrasinal que coincida coa súa consulta
NoSearchResults.description: Used in the search tab when no entries match the search query

NoSearchQuery.message: Escriba na caixa de busca para atopar contrasinais
NoSearchQuery.description: Used in the search tab when there is no search query

NoCollectedPasswords.description: Used in the collected tab when no new passwords have been found

AddPasswordForCurrentTab.message: Engadir credenciais para a lapela actual
AddPasswordForCurrentTab.description: Used in the collected tab for the option to add a blank entry with just the url of the current tab

NoServerItems.description: Used in the browse tab when a server has no entries to list

BrowseNoServers.description: Used in the browse tab when no accounts/servers are available

SearchPlaceholder.description: Placeholder text of the search box

MiningItemIsNew.description: Text shown in a collected password that is new to tell the user that it is a new passwor

LabelLabel.description: Label for the name of a password entry

LabelPassword.description: Label for the password of a password entry

LabelUsername.description: Label for the username of a password entry

LabelHidden.description: Label for the checkbox to mark a password entry as private or hidden in the webapp

LabelUrl.description: Label for of a field that contains an url (used in collected password or server info)

LabelUser.description: Label for the username of in the server info in the browse tab

LabelPasswords.description: Label for the password count in the server info in the browse tab

LabelFolders.description: Label for the folder count in the server info in the browse tab

LabelFolder.description: Label for the folder of this password.

LabelCreated.description: Label for the creation time of this password.

LabelEdited.description: Label for the last edit time of this password.

LabelNotes.description: Label for the notes of this password.

LabelServerVersion.description: Label for the nextcloud server version in the server info in the browse tab

LabelAppVersion.description: Label for the passwords app version in the server info in the browse tab

AppLabelString.description: Value for the passwords app version in the server info in the browse tab

PlaceholderPassword.description: Placeholder text in the master password field of the server authorization dialog

PlaceholderToken.description: Placeholder text in the master password field of the server authorization dialog

ButtonLogin.description: The text of the login button of the server authorization dialog

AuthorizationFailedTitle.description: Title of the toast notification when the login attempt was unsuccessful

AuthorizationFailedText.message: Foi denegado o acceso á base de datos de contrasinais co acceso fornecido
AuthorizationFailedText.description: Text of the toast notification when the login attempt was unsuccessful

NotifyNewPasswordTitle.description: Title of the system notification when a new password was detected

NotifyNewPasswordText.message: Foi detectado un novo contrasinal para «$LABEL$».
NotifyNewPasswordText.description: Text of the system notification when a new password was detected. Used in Chrome where the notification has buttons to save or view the password

ButtonSave.description: The save button of a password detection system notification

ButtonMore.description: The more options button of a password detection system notification which opens the popup with the form which shows all password details

ButtonClose.description: The title of the close button of a toast notification

ToastServerCheckTitle.description: Title of the toast notification when an account was disabled because the server uses an outdated and unsupported version of the passwords app

PropertyPassword.description: Label of the property password of the password entry used in PasswordPropertyCopied

PropertyUrl.description: Label of the property url of the password entry used in PasswordPropertyCopied

SettingsThemeId.description: Label of the option to choose the current theme in the extension settings

ValidationToken.description: Name of the account token field in account validation message. This value is used when the user attempts to save an account with an invalid token

ValidationInvalidTimeout.message: O tempo de peche debe ser unha das opcións indicadas.
ValidationInvalidTimeout.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save an account but the timeout is not within the predefined range

ValidationConnectionError.message: Ao tentar conectarse a $URL$ produciuse o erro $ERROR$.
ValidationConnectionError.description: Validation message when the user attempts to save an account but the connection attempt resulted in any kind of error (including internal extension errors)

LabelCustomFields.description: Label for the custom fields of this password

LabelTags.description: Label for the tag count in the server info in the browse tab

ServerLabelString.description: Value for the nextcloud server version in the server info in the browse tab

PropertyUsername.description: Label of the property username of the password entry used in PasswordPropertyCopied

MiningItemIsUpdate.message: Esta semella ser unha actualización de «$PASSWORD$»
MiningItemIsUpdate.description: Text shown in a collected password that is an update of an existing password

TokenRequestFailed.message: Produciuse un fallo na solicitude de testemuño
TokenRequestFailed.description: Title of the toast notification when the request for a two factor auth token failed. The text will be the error message.
